Placeholder so git tracks this empty directory.

Per `spec.md`, this path is the canonical hostPath source for
the kind worker's `/var/local/node1` mount. In this repo the
active path is `infra/data/node1/` (the tofu config defaults
`data_root = "../data"`, which from `infra/tofu/` resolves
there); see `AGENTS.md` §7 for the path-resolution note.